    "summary": "I am a results-driven finance professional with over a decade of experience shaping financial strategies and driving transformative initiatives for global organizations. Throughout my career, I've had the privilege of contributing to the success of esteemed companies and witnessing the positive impact of strategic financial leadership.\n\nMy international journey began at msg global solutions SEE ltd, where I served as a Head of Finance, formerly a Financial Controller and Tax Accountant. Leading financial management, controlling, and FP&A, I implemented innovative forecasting and management reporting systems that streamlined processes, ensured error-free outcomes, and empowered data-driven decision-making.\n\nAs a Financial Controller at AstraZeneca UK Limited Belgrade, I played a pivotal role in optimizing financial performance and enhancing business operations. I successfully conducted performance reviews, providing monthly deep-dive analyses of cost and revenue variances, enabling timely and well-informed decisions.\n\nAs a Regional Financial Controller for the CEE region at AstraZeneca UK Limited, I harmonized internal controls across Europe, reviewed over 1350 controls across 23 companies, and provided valuable support for the ME closing process.\n\nI also played a significant role in AstraZeneca's global finance transformation as a Process-Technology Design SME for R2R and Controls. My contribution to the implementation of the Blackline project streamlined balance sheet reconciliation processes across numerous business units and company codes, ensuring enhanced controls and compliance with SOX and Internal Control Framework requirements.\n\nFurthermore, at AstraZeneca Pharma Poland Sp. z o.o., I held the position of Controlling Finance Manager within the esteemed Global Group Finance Team.\n\nMy passion for driving efficiency and delivering actionable insights has been a driving force throughout my career. I thrive on continuous improvement and have consistently been part of teams leading process redesigns and improvement initiatives.\n\nMy expertise lies in financial planning and analysis, management reporting, process optimization, internal controls, and business transformation. I am committed to making a positive impact through my financial acumen and strategic vision.\n\nLet's connect and explore opportunities for collaboration. I'm always open to engaging in meaningful discussions with fellow professionals and industry.",
